core::slice::<impl [T]>::is_empty.doc:
Returns `true` if the slice has a length of 0.

# Examples

```
let a = [1, 2, 3];
assert!(!a.is_empty());

let b: &[i32] = &[];
assert!(b.is_empty());
```

